# Keep the build context small and never ship secrets or build artifacts.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/build
**/.output
**/src/generated
.git
.github
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store

# Secrets — env is injected by the host at runtime.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Local-only
DEPLOYMENT.md
docs
**/*.test.ts
